description: Once you enable the skill, say "Alexa, ask the TDLG for legal advice" to hear a humorous, tongue-in-cheek response.  Note: This skill is for novelty purposes only, and in no way constitutes actual legal advice.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask the TDLG for legal advice.
Alexa, ask the TDLG for advice.

name: Ask the TDLG
shortDescription: Ask the TDLG (Technology & Digital Law Group) for legal advice and receive a tongue-in-cheek response.  Novelty purposes only.
